{"tid":1889294,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"匿名郵箱","createTime":"2020-02-20T14:57:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-25T20:32:33.000Z","uid":283503,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"86b35b0f0bad708937f99e193cfb607ba1b9c444","tid":1889294,"uid":283503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T14:57:54.000Z","msg":"大家好！其實好耐好耐之前我都搞過類似嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過呢排Home Office所以多咗時間可以聽吓大家心事<br />\n<br />\n其實形式好簡單，你可以用自己個電郵/ 開一個新嘅電郵send E-mail俾我<br />\n通常啲人都會打好大段嘢俾我，講吓自己背景/故事/遇到嘅困難<br />\n當然啦，有問題都可以一齊討論吓<br />\n我通常睇完都會覆翻一段嘢俾你<br />\n<br />\n你可以當係識筆友又好，搵人傾吓計都好<br />\n無論你係男女老幼咩背景都好，我都會一視同仁<br />\n當然所有內容我都唔會公開啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我個電郵:happypakconsultation@gmail.com"},{"pid":"f8924656e26dfb0bc53c3f6b539caa1eb78903b5","tid":1889294,"uid":241816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T15:12:10.000Z","msg":"好似幾得意咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98017e1e9c0c2ca0021a1008fba7d4fc9c2483e1","tid":1889294,"uid":283503,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f8924656e26dfb0bc53c3f6b539caa1eb78903b5","tid":1889294,"uid":241816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T15:12:10.000Z","msg":"好似幾得意咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T15:52:28.000Z","msg":"雖然用緊啲舊方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為嗰時唔興用TG嗰啲嘢<br />\n反而會有耐性去打一大篇野<br />\n而且私隱度高<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4eda90cac5fd63d5672e60df7dcf74559bdfc24","tid":1889294,"uid":283503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T17:52:34.000Z","msg":"訓前一推<br />\n岩岩覆咗一位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23bc403dec48bf472b77d0f8aaf00f119378dee7","tid":1889294,"uid":255269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"